<p><strong>Sources</strong> <Link to="/source/inner_sea_races">Inner Sea Races</Link><br/>You were bullied in your youth but supported by one or more good friends, impressing upon you the importance of teamwork. You gain a +1 trait bonus on damage rolls against foes you flank.</p>
